      "content": "Hey, I'm studying for my Con Law exam and I'm a bit stuck on the 2nd Amendment stuff. In your opinion, is the current Supreme Court's interpretation of the 2nd Amendment actually an accurate reflection of what the Founders intended, or is it just judicial overreach?",
